        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>In ten years time, my life will be easy! My children will be adults, so i could stop to work. Everyday, i will go to walk and after i could read a lot of books. I will go to travel too. I want to plant many flowers and trees. Sometimes, i'll go to see my friends and my sisters.</p>
            </div>
